About Us

Strategy





Strategy



Safestyle UK's strategy is to focus primarily on the UK homeowner replacement windows and doors market.
The Directors believe Safestyle is the lowest cost national retailer and manufacturer of PVCu windows and doors for this market and this position will enable Safestyle to benefit from improvements in the wider economy and other market opportunities.
We aim to expand our geographical representation by targeting a further increase in the South and South East of England.  Additional market opportunities are being pursued with a new replacement conservatory product.






