Building Products & Construction Materials




Company Description


Safestyle UK Plc engages in selling, manufacturing and installing polyvinyl chloride un-plasticized windows and doors for the homeowner replacement market. Its products include upvc windows, legacy sash, bay and heritage. The company was founded on December 22, 1992 and is headquartered in Bradford, the United Kingdom.




Website


http://www.safestyle-windows.co.uk






